snippet.title: Vortex Point 7 - Walkthrough
snippet.description:
Play the game at http://carmelgames.com/vortex-point-7-waddington-swamp/

The infamous Dr. Prescott visits Vortex Point to explore the mysterious Waddington Swamp. While Kevin helps him navigating around the swamp, they discover the true story behind the Waddington Swamp.
